# ARI Dashboard Rules for Cursor AI

## Stack
- React 19 + TypeScript
- Vite 6 for build
- TanStack Query for data fetching
- Tailwind CSS 4 for styling

## Design System
- Dark theme (gray-950 background)
- Purple accent (#8b5cf6)
- Color palette: emerald (success), red (error), amber (warning), cyan (info)
- Cards with hover effects (.card-hover)
- Rounded corners (rounded-xl for cards)

## Component Patterns
```tsx
// Always use safe array checks
const safeData = Array.isArray(data) ? data : [];

// Always handle loading/error states
if (isLoading) return <Skeleton />;
if (isError) return <ErrorState onRetry={refetch} />;
if (safeData.length === 0) return <EmptyState />;
```

## API
- Gateway: http://127.0.0.1:3141
- All endpoints return typed responses
- Auto-refresh with refetchInterval

## Pages
- Home: System overview
- Agents: 5-agent council (CORE, GUARDIAN, PLANNER, EXECUTOR, MEMORY)
- Governance: 13-member council, 5 constitutional rules
- Audit: SHA-256 hash chain visualization
- Memory: Provenance-tracked knowledge
- Tools: Three-layer permission display

## Commands
```bash
npm run dev      # Dev server :5173
npm run build    # Production build
npm run lint     # ESLint
```
